MOUNTAIN VIEW, CALIF. -- Pixim, a fabless semiconductor company that produces digital image sensors for digital cameras and other devices, is expected to announce the closing of $16.5 million in Series C financing. New funds will be used for product development, marketing, and sales. [more.. <http://professional.venturewire.com/prostory.asp>]
